### MyTodoList — CRUD HTTP Requests
### Usar con extensión "REST Client" de VS Code (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ============================================================
### ToDoItem CRUD
### ============================================================

### 1. Listar todas las tareas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Obtener tarea por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Crear nueva tarea
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Nueva tarea desde VS Code",
  "done": false
}

###

### 4. Actualizar tarea (cambiar ID según necesidad)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Tarea actualizada desde VS Code",
  "done": true
}

###

### 5. Eliminar tarea
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1

###

### 6. Probar 404 - ID inexistente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/99999
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Probar validación - descripción vacía (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "",
  "done": false
}

### ============================================================
### User CRUD
### ============================================================

###

### 8. Listar usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Crear usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "5512345678",
  "userPassword": "miPassword123"
}

###

### 10. Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Actualizar usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "5587654321",
  "userPassword": "nuevoPassword456"
}

###

### 12. Eliminar usuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1

### ============================================================
### Legacy endpoints (backward compatibility)
### ============================================================

###

### Listar tareas (legacy)
GET {{baseUrl}}/todolist

###

### Crear tarea (legacy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/todolist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Tarea legacy"
}

